; Coverage for amount.cc
; IF_DEBUG("amount.convert") block in stream_out_mpq that prints the
; rational number before conversion. Triggered by --debug amount.convert.
; The 2>/dev/null suppresses debug output on stderr to avoid timestamp
; matching issues in the test harness.

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.50
    Assets:Cash

test bal --debug amount.convert 2>/dev/null
             $-10.50  Assets:Cash
              $10.50  Expenses:Food
--------------------
                   0
end test
